    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Someone needs your help, but you don't have enough time to save her. Leap into the past to succeed, but don't trigger a time paradox. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Time Riggers is a turn-based time-leap puzzle game that will challenge your spatio-temporal logic and memory. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135920/extras/56e7c0b77771e96382897f687a35fb4d.poster.avif?t=1732825132\" width=320 height=96 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135920/extras/56e7c0b77771e96382897f687a35fb4d.webm?t=1732825132\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135920/extras/56e7c0b77771e96382897f687a35fb4d.mp4?t=1732825132\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Goal </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Activate the switches and reach the exit before the time is up. Each move costs 1 second. The time limit is indicated by the watch. Leap into to past to succeed.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >How to leap into the past</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Use your Time-Pack  <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135920/extras/06c6bfa9ee2b6181245e88c5f0090083.apng?t=1732825132\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135920/extras/06c6bfa9ee2b6181245e88c5f0090083.poster.avif?t=1732825132\" class=\"bb_img\" width=28 height=28 /></picture></span>. When you do so, you will see your past self.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Don't run into your past self, that would trigger a time paradox.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Each leap in the past costs some energy. The amount of energy left is indicated with the gauge.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Content</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 23 puzzles :  13 easy, 6 medium, 4 difficult puzzles.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 3 scoring levels.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Includes 1 hour in gameplay.</p></li></ul>",
